title: Ep 526 | Phil Rages at the Drug Destroying Young Lives & Missy Catches Jase White-Handed
description:
Kyle Thompson of the "Undaunted Life" podcast joins the studio to discuss problematic worldviews and why men should strive to have reverence and fear of the Lord. Phil talks about the drug that is responsible for a stunning number of deaths and how it's destroying young American lives. Jase tells a funny story about getting carried away with a family-sized bag of Missy's powdered donuts. Al talks about his granddaughter and her jiu-jitsu skills.
